snippet.title: The Rewinder 2 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Rewinder 2 is an action adventure game inspried by eastern methology. As the last known rewinder, you'll wield the powers of Sizhi god to explore disrrupted villages, dungeons and save people from their dreams.
